<p><strong>39.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1230">SCP-1230</a> &quot;A Hero is Born&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpixel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1350583); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1350583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="MrPixel" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1350583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpixel" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1350583); return false;">MrPixel</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;As sweet as dreams may be, eventually we all have to wake up.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>40.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1252">SCP-1252</a> &quot;A Half-Formed Idea&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;">SoullessSingularity</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Could you find her and tell her I'm okay? We got separated in an accident and I don't want her to worry.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<p><strong>41.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1342">SCP-1342</a> &quot;To the Makers of Music&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flameshirt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1467808); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1467808&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="FlameShirt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1467808)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flameshirt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1467808); return false;">FlameShirt</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;From one maker of music to another-&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>42.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4974">SCP-4974</a> &quot;The Mouse SCP&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;">Tanhony</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>SCP-4974 is an anomalous organism aesthetically identical to the character of Pikachu from the Pokémon media franchise.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Warning: this is not a nice trip down memory lane/of nostalgia.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>43.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1960">SCP-1960</a> &quot;Neptunian Text Messages&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tiger66261" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1373135); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1373135&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="Tiger66261" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1373135)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tiger66261" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1373135); return false;">Tiger66261</a></span> rewritten by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(362048); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=362048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="Smapti" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=362048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smapti" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(362048); return false;">Smapti</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Recurring themes in SCP-1960 communications include feelings of fear, isolation, and discomfort.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>44.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-1166">SCP-1166</a> &quot;Perfect Lab Specimen&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;">Kalinin</a></span> (Original account deleted as seen in the articles history, found this in Helen her metadata.)</p>
<blockquote>
<p>SCP-1166: (written response) Foundation makes dokter ██████ stop hurting we. foundation not hu8rt we?</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Dr. ████████: I am not going to hurt you SCP-1166.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>45.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2516">SCP-2516</a> &quot;The Man from Taured&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dododevil" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1854139); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1854139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="DodoDevil" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1854139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dododevil" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1854139); return false;">DodoDevil</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;Yeah, how long are you going to keep me locked up in here? I’ve got a family waiting for me.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<p><strong>46.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5117">SCP-5117</a> &quot;<span style="color: red">Alex?</span> I’m Lonely&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greyve" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4045981); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4045981&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="Greyve" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4045981)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greyve" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4045981); return false;">Greyve</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;you can not leave me I am lonely all I am is loneliness and I know you know lonely because you are lonely and loneliness is all I am&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>47.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4361">SCP-4361</a> &quot;Red is Her Favorite Color&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kybard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5717239); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5717239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="Kybard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5717239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kybard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5717239); return false;">Kybard</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;not cries for help. Cries to stop&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>48.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4686">SCP-4686</a> &quot;Hugs 4 Everyone&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/allerarey" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4386350); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4386350&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="AlleraRey " style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4386350)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/allerarey" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4386350); return false;">AlleraRey</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;I really needed that. Thanks.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>49.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-4274">SCP-4274</a> &quot;The Lonely Angel&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crystalmonarch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2951031); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2951031&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="CrystalMonarch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2951031)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crystalmonarch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2951031); return false;">CrystalMonarch</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;He may think himself alone on this world of ours but he can still see it's beauty. And so long as he can find the strength to continue, so can I.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>50.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5975">SCP-5975</a> &quot;The Cycle Keeps Spinning&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1777811); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1777811&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610002657" alt="weizhong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1777811)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1777811); return false;">weizhong</a></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p>&quot;<em>I miss you. I really, really miss you. I know why we have to stay in isolation but…I still really miss you.</em>&quot;</p>
</blockquote>
